title: PM approves national data strategy to accelerate digital government
combined_text: PM approves national data strategy to accelerate digital government. en.vietnamplus.vn.
summary: Vietnam's PM approved a national data strategy aiming for 80% of public services online by 2025. The strategy prioritizes data infrastructure, focusing on data collection, sharing, and security, hoping for better digital government. Vietnam targets 100% of national databases connected and open by 2030, fostering data-driven innovation.
